    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Appendix DS20 / ES40 / ES45</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The larger Tsunami-family machines are planned but not yet modeled or validated in EmulatR. They are recorded here so the platform roadmap is explicit; none of them currently reaches the <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> prompt.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">DS20</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Planned. DS20 is not yet modeled or validated. A platform manifest and reference notes will be added once the model exists.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">ES40</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Planned. The platform manifest <text styleclass="Code Example">es40_platform.json</text> is scaffolded, but the platform has not yet been driven to the <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> prompt. To be validated and documented.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">ES45</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Planned. The platform manifest <text styleclass="Code Example">es45_platform.json</text> (EV67 / 21264A) is scaffolded but not yet validated. To be documented once it boots.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Note that the compressed firmware oracle work (host_decompressor) was developed against <text styleclass="Code Example">es45_v7_3.exe</text>, so the ES45 firmware image decompresses correctly even though the full platform is not yet driven; what remains is the device and chipset modeling around it.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
